room_title: Escape room "The Morgue" by All Locked Up in Los Angeles
room_address: 18914 Soledad Canyon Rd Santa Clarita, CA 91351
room_description: Chapter 4: After Aunt Debbie's, you walked away with a key. This key had a tag that read "Brookhart City Morgue." This can only lead to bad things. Time to finish the Scott story that you started in The Classroom, and time to find out what is really going on with your neighbor. Can you handle this one? It's a real morgue; so freezers, death, body parts, and smells that might make you cringe. Come to The Morgue to find out what Scott has been up to this whole time. Bring some bravery and maybe even a Bible. Who knows what Death has in store for you and your team.
